					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Alright, so this dragged pretty heavy for me right up until the last bit of the transcript, during which point the article itself just kind of clicked together. The mention of Nemesis, and the idea of humans potentially willing this being into existence (unless your Anomalous Columbo is supposed to BE NEMESIS) to make sure justice is done is a thing I can get behind.</p> <p>+1 kinch</p> 
				 	]]>
